flowchart TD
    A[dependency_edges.json] --> B[load_architecture_rules<br/>architecture_rules.yaml]
    A --> C[classify_edge loop]
    B --> C

    C --> D{Rule match?}

    D -->|rule found, decision=allowed| E[intentional]
    D -->|rule found, decision=forbidden| F[blocked]
    D -->|no rule, edge.allowed=False| G[accidental]
    D -->|no rule, edge.allowed=True| H[unknown]

    F --> I[rule_forbidden_dependency_edge]
    I --> J[Raw Finding Dict<br/>category=drift, evidence=edge]
    J --> K[emit_findings<br/>findings.json]
    K --> L[emit_dispatch<br/>dispatch_queue.json]

    E --> M[Drift Report Summary]
    F --> M
    G --> M
    H --> M

    M --> N[drift_report.json<br/>schema-validated]

    subgraph CI Drift Gate
        N --> O{Any blocked edge<br/>at P0 or P1?}
        O -->|yes| P[drift_gate.py exits 1<br/>BUILD FAILS]
        O -->|no| Q[drift_gate.py exits 0<br/>BUILD PASSES]
    end
